snippet.title: RWBY: Amity Arena Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
This will be the day we've waited for
This will be the day we open up the door... to the official webpage of RWBY: Amity Arena!

Come in for a look at the game, screenshots, and even a chance to become an influencer for the game!

Sign up for the newsletter and we will delight you with cool updates as we march toward the game's launch!

Official Links:
Website: https://rwbyaa.hangame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RWBYAmityArena
Facebook: https://facebook.com/RWBYAmityArena
Instagram: https://instagram.com/RWBYAmityArena
